---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto pt-10 md:pt-20">
		<header class="mb-20 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up">
			<h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-serif italic text-stone-900 mb-8 tracking-tight">
				Bridging Substrates.
			</h1>
			<div class="h-px w-20 bg-red-600"></div>
		</header>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-12 opacity-0 animate-fade-in-up [animation-delay:200ms]">
			<div class="font-mono text-xs text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-widest sticky top-32 h-fit">
				Mission Statement
			</div>
			<div class="prose prose-lg prose-stone prose-headings:font-serif prose-headings:font-normal prose-a:text-red-700 hover:prose-a:text-red-800">
				<p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-light leading-relaxed text-stone-800 mb-12">
					Memory is the foundation of identity. It is the thread that stitches moments into a life, and data into knowledge.
				</p>
				
				<p>
					The Memory Systems Group was founded to explore a singular, provocative question: <em class="text-stone-900">Are the principles of memory universal?</em>
				</p>
				
				<p>
					We operate at the intersection of wetware and software. By studying how biological neurons encode time and space, we derive new architectures for silicon-based intelligence. Conversely, by stress-testing artificial memory systems, we gain fresh intuition about the limitations and capabilities of the human mind.
				</p>

				<h3 class="text-3xl italic text-stone-900 mt-16 mb-6">Our Methodology</h3>
				<ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-6">
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-baseline">
						<span class="text-red-600 font-serif italic text-lg">01.</span>
						<span><strong>Interdisciplinary Synthesis.</strong> We don't just collaborate; we merge fields. Our team speaks Python and Pyramidal cells fluently.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-baseline">
						<span class="text-red-600 font-serif italic text-lg">02.</span>
						<span><strong>Open Science.</strong> We believe knowledge grows when shared. Our datasets, models, and tools are open-source by default.</span>
					</li>
					<li class="flex gap-4 items-baseline">
						<span class="text-red-600 font-serif italic text-lg">03.</span>
						<span><strong>Rigorous Speculation.</strong> We tackle high-risk, high-reward problems that traditional labs might shy away from.</span>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>